Valérie Donzelli https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Val%C3%A9rie_Donzelli 0 Valérie Donzelli (born 2 March 1973) is a French actress, filmmaker and screenwriter. She has directed five feature films and two short films since 2008, including the film Declaration of War (2011).
